---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Trust Architecture — SPA earn-defi.com"
  description="How SPA is structured, who controls what, and how your capital is handled. 9 key questions answered for allocators."
  canonical="https://earn-defi.com/trust"
>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="flex items-center justify-between px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-5 border-b border-white/5">
    <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2 text-white/60 hover:text-white transition-colors">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5 3 12m0 0 7.5-7.5M3 12h18"/>
      </svg>
      <span class="text-sm">Back to earn-defi.com</span>
    </a>
    <span class="text-xs text-white/20 font-mono">trust</span>
  </nav>

  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12">
      <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-3">Architecture</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Trust Architecture</h1>
      <p class="text-white/50 text-lg leading-relaxed">
        How SPA is structured, who controls what, and how your capital is handled.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro -->
    <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-6 mb-12 text-sm text-white/60 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        SPA operates as a paper trading system through go-live. This page documents the control
        architecture, data flows, and operational safeguards that govern how the system works.
        Transparency is the product.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Custody Model -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Custody Model</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400/60 mt-2"></span>
          <p><strong class="text-white/80">Paper trading phase:</strong> no real capital involved. Virtual $100,000 USDC portfolio.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400/60 mt-2"></span>
          <p><strong class="text-white/80">Live phase (planned):</strong> self-custodial model. Users retain control of assets via Gnosis Safe multisig. SPA operates as an authorised keeper with limited execution rights.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400/60 mt-2"></span>
          <p>SPA does not hold user funds in a centralised custodian.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400/60 mt-2"></span>
          <p><strong class="text-white/80">Keeper permissions:</strong> rebalance within approved whitelist only. Cannot withdraw to external addresses.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 9 Key Questions -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">The 9 Key Questions</h2>
      <p class="text-xs text-white/30 mb-8">Key questions about the system architecture.</p>

      <div class="space-y-6">

        <!-- Q1 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q1</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Who can change the strategy?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            Strategy parameters are defined in RiskPolicy v1.0. Changes require a documented ADR
            (Architecture Decision Record), version bump, and re-run of GoLiveChecker. No undocumented changes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q2 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q2</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Who can change RiskPolicy?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            RiskPolicy changes require explicit versioning. Currently v1.0. Any change produces a new
            version with documented rationale. Changelog is public in repository.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q3 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q3</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Who can pause deposits?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            Kill switch can be triggered by: (1) automated drawdown gate (&minus;5% monthly),
            (2) manual trigger by operator. Both paths are logged. Kill switch moves portfolio to cash buffer.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q4 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q4</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Who can close positions?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            In paper trading: automated rebalancer only, within RiskPolicy gates. In live phase: keeper
            (automated) within approved permissions + multisig emergency override.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q5 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q5</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Who can upgrade contracts?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            Live phase: multisig required for any contract upgrade. Timelock TBD before go-live.
            Paper trading phase: no live contracts deployed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q6 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q6</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Can a human override a risk gate?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            No. In paper trading phase, blocked rebalances are logged but not executed. The gate result
            is final. Manual override capability is explicitly excluded from keeper permissions.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q7 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q7</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Is there a multisig, and who are the signers?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            Gnosis Safe multisig planned for live phase. Signer composition and threshold TBD before
            go-live. Will be published in this document before August 1, 2026.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q8 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q8</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">Where can I see all logs?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
            Dashboard &rarr; Trades tab (all rebalance events), Dashboard &rarr; Risk Blocks tab
            (all blocked rebalances), and a version-controlled audit log (JSON logs, ADRs, RiskPolicy versions).
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Q9 -->
        <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-green-400/70 font-mono mb-2">Q9</p>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white mb-2">What happens during an incident?</h3>
          <div class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed space-y-1">
            <p>1. Kill switch activates if drawdown gate fires.</p>
            <p>2. Operator notified via monitoring alerts.</p>
            <p>3. Portfolio moves to cash buffer.</p>
            <p>4. Incident documented and published.</p>
            <p>5. No resumption until root cause identified.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- KYC / Identity Verification -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Identity Verification</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-6">
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400/60 mt-2"></span>
            <p>No identity verification required to view strategies or dashboard.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400/60 mt-2"></span>
            <p>Currently paper-only — no deposits. In any future live phase, verification procedures will be documented here.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-green-400/60 mt-2"></span>
            <p>This is a paper research project. No funds are managed. See architecture above for planned live phase controls.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Incident Communication -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Incident Communication</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          In the private MVP phase, incident communication is handled directly via Telegram and email.
          Response owner: Yurii. Public status page and formal SLA will be added before public launch.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contract Transparency -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Contract Transparency</h2>
      <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
          We publish the list of approved DeFi protocols we work with. Operational wallet addresses
          and SPA-specific contract addresses will be published after security audit completion
          (planned Q3 2026).
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Operational Model -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Operational Model</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/30 font-mono mb-1">Daily Cycle</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60">Scan &rarr; Gate &rarr; Rebalance (automated)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/30 font-mono mb-1">LLM in Execution</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60">None. Zero AI in the decision path.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/30 font-mono mb-1">Decision Logic</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60">All decisions deterministic and logged</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-white/30 font-mono mb-1">Paper Trading</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-white/60">No real transactions — all operations simulated</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Live Monitors -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-6 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Live Monitors</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <a href="/#live-stats" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 hover:border-green-400/30 transition-colors group">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 group-hover:text-white">GoLiveChecker</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40">25/26 criteria currently passing (NOT READY)</p>
          </div>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-white/20 group-hover:text-green-400/60">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/#live-stats" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 hover:border-green-400/30 transition-colors group">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 group-hover:text-white">Risk Blocks</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40">All blocked rebalances logged</p>
          </div>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-white/20 group-hover:text-green-400/60">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/#live-stats" class="flex items-center justify-between rounded-lg border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 hover:border-green-400/30 transition-colors group">
          <div>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/80 group-hover:text-white">Paper APY</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-white/40">Tracked daily since June 10, 2026</p>
          </div>
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-white/20 group-hover:text-green-400/60">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 4.5 21 12m0 0-7.5 7.5M21 12H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact -->
    <section class="mb-14">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 pb-3 border-b border-white/8">Contact</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
        For due diligence inquiries: <a href="mailto:yuriycooleshov@gmail.com" class="text-green-400/80 hover:text-green-400 underline underline-offset-2">yuriycooleshov@gmail.com</a>
      </p>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />

</Layout>
